Another community meetup in Colombia was held in Cúcuta, a city bordering Venezuela. Venezuela is a country that uses cryptocurrencies as a means of payment and it’s exciting to see them discussing Cardano.  Read more from organizer, Javier, here:  https://t.co/4dPNxl8e9o

When $BTC is moving down, many alts are correlated and move down too. When $BTC goes up, many alts are correlated and will move with $BTC upwards.  In that way: if you expect $BTC to go down, short the alts (like $ADA). If you expect $BTC to go up, long the alts.  Gaining $BTC :)
